      "content": "```python\ndef parse_packet(pkt):\n    if len(pkt) != 4:\n        return None\n    cmd = pkt[0]\n    val = int.from_bytes(pkt[1:4], 'little')\n    return {'cmd': cmd, 'val': val}\n\ndef test_parser():\n    # test 1: cmd 1, val 500\n    pkt1 = b'\\x01\\xf4\\x01\\x00'\n    assert parse_packet(pkt1) == {'cmd': 1, 'val': 500}\n\n    # test 2: cmd 5, val 10\n    pkt2 = b'\\x05\\x0a\\x00\\x00'\n    assert parse_packet(pkt2) == {'cmd': 5, 'val': 10}\n    \n    # test 3: cmd 10, val 65535\n    pkt3 = b'\\x0a\\xff\\xff\\xff'\n    assert parse_packet(pkt3) == {'cmd': 10, 'val': 65535}\n\nparse_packet = parse_packet\ntest_parser()\nprint(\"All tests passed!\")\n```",
